---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
---
<Base
  bodyClass="brand-page rollout-page"
  title="Privacy Policy | Joshua Tree Health"
  description="How Joshua Tree Health collects, uses, and protects your information."
  robots="noindex, follow"
>
  <PageHero
    eyebrow="Legal"
    art="mark"
    title="Privacy Policy"
    sub="This explains what we collect on this website, how we use it, and the choices you have."
  />

  <section class="section" aria-labelledby="privacy-title">
    <div class="container-x">
      <h2 id="privacy-title" class="sr-only">Privacy policy</h2>
      <div class="prose" data-reveal>
        <p class="lead">We collect only what we need to respond to you and improve this site, and we never sell your information.</p>
        <p class="form__note">Last updated June 2026.</p>

        <h2>Information we collect</h2>
        <p>When you submit a form, such as a callback or contact request, we collect the information you provide. This typically includes your name, phone number, email, your teen's age, and any message. We ask you <strong>not</strong> to include medical details in website forms; clinical information is gathered securely by phone or in person.</p>
        <p>We also collect limited, standard analytics (such as pages visited and general device type) to understand how the site is used. We do not use this to identify you personally.</p>

        <h2>How we use it</h2>
        <p>We use your information to respond to your request, schedule a call, verify insurance benefits, and improve our services. We will only contact you about your inquiry and our programs, and you can opt out at any time.</p>

        <h2>How we protect it</h2>
        <p>We use reasonable administrative, technical, and physical safeguards to protect your information. Protected health information collected through treatment is handled under HIPAA and our separate <strong>Notice of Privacy Practices</strong>, which governs clinical records.</p>

        <h2>Sharing</h2>
        <p>We do not sell your personal information. We share it only with service providers who help us operate, such as our scheduling or form tools, and only as needed to serve you or when required by law.</p>

        <h2>Your choices</h2>
        <p>You can ask us to access, correct, or delete the information you've submitted through this website by emailing <a href="mailto:admissions@jtreehealth.com">admissions@jtreehealth.com</a>. You can also decline non-essential cookies in your browser.</p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>Questions about this policy? Email <a href="mailto:admissions@jtreehealth.com">admissions@jtreehealth.com</a> or call <a href="tel:+19193355053">(919) 335-5053</a>.</p>

        <p class="form__note" style="margin-top:2.5rem;">This page is a website privacy policy and does not replace our HIPAA Notice of Privacy Practices. It should be reviewed by legal counsel before launch.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
